entries.title: Arizona Republicans walk out on Katie Hobbs's first State of the State address
entries.description: Republican lawmakers in Arizona wasted no time letting new Democratic Gov. Katie Hobbs know how they feel about her Monday as they walked out of Hobbs's first State of the State address.

entries.title: Georgia House elects Burns as speaker
entries.description: (The Center Square) — The Georgia House kicked off business on Monday by electing state Rep. Jon Burns, R-Newington, as its new speaker.
